If you’ve known me long enough, you’ll know that my go to beverage is a hot cup of coffee! And since Ashwin shares this love for coffee with me, it made perfect sense to bring home this fabulous coffee maker from @morphyrichardsindia .

The New Europa coffee maker is great not just for espressos but with the frothing nozzle I can also make delicious cups of cappuccinos! Yay! 

I love the size of it, it fits in beautifully atop our small sideboard, adding charm to our little coffee station here.

A wonderful gift for our home. ♥️
